Steps:
1. Open GraphQL xAPI endpoint
2. Execute query:
query {
  products(
    storeId: "mystore1"
    cultureName: "en-US"
    currencyCode: "USD"
    productIds: "<product-id>"
  ) {
    items {
      name
      id
      prices {
        list {
          formattedAmountWithoutPoint
        }
        pricelistId
        actual {
          formattedAmount
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
3. Verify response contains correct price data

Expected Result:
Response contains:
{
  "data": {
    "products": {
      "items": [{
        "name": "test prod"
        "id": "<product-id>"
        "prices": [{
          "list": {
            "formattedAmountWithoutPoint": "$111"
          }
          "pricelistId": "<pricelist-id>"
          "actual": {
            "formattedAmount": "$111.00"
          }
        }]
      }]
    }
  }
}
